data.description: Price correction!  Motivated sellers!  Updated landscaping!!This is the one you have been waiting for!  One level home on park like 2.5 private acres with 2 massive primary suites.  One suite overlooks the front yard and one the backyard!  Take your pick! Great set up for multi-gen families.  The home boasts 3 bedrooms, 3 and 1/2 baths with a large office/den with built in bookshelves and desk. You will relish the vaulted ceilings, large windows and formal dining room.  The covered patio has room for everyone to enjoy the peaceful backyard.  Take a stroll down to the creek to new adventures!  The large shop with a 10 ft door has room for all of your toys/workshops/storage needs! Priced below tax assessment value.  Instant equity! Ask your agent (or me!) for the virtual tour of the shop!
